  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability and Effectiveness of Natalizumab in Adolescents With Active Crohn's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, International, Multicenter, Open Label Study of the Safety, Tolerability and Effectiveness of Three Intravenous Infusions of Antegren (Natalizumab) in Adolescents With Moderately to Severely Active Crohn's Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
