  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Male and female patients, 12-17 years of age, who have at least a six-month history of
        Crohn's disease and who are currently experiencing moderately to severely active Crohn's
        disease. Females must not be breastfeeding or pregnant, and must not become pregnant during
        the study.
      </textblock>
